	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">为推进和规范预决算信息公开工作，强化社会监督，促进依法理财，转变政府职能，建立透明预算制度，根据《中华人民共和国预算法》、《中华人民共和国政府信息公开条例》（国务院令第<SPAN lang=EN-US>492</SPAN>号）、《中共中央办公厅 国务院办公厅印发<SPAN lang=EN-US>&lt;</SPAN>关于进一步推进预算公开工作的意见<SPAN lang=EN-US>&gt;</SPAN>的通知》（中办发</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">﹝</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt" lang=EN-US>2016</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">﹞</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt" lang=EN-US>13</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">号）、《江苏省预决算信息公开管理暂行办法》（苏办发</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">﹝</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt" lang=EN-US>2016</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">﹞</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US>37</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">号）、《<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>年昆山市市级预决算信息公开工作方案》（昆财字（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>）<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>号）<A name=_GoBack></A>等有关规定，结合我委实际，制定本方案。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">一、基本原则<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（一）坚持以公开为常态、不公开为例外。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">除涉及国家秘密的信息外，使用财政资金的部门和单位应当积极推动本部门预决算公开。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（二）坚持明确和落实责任。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">各部门各单位应当依法主动公开预决算信息。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（三）坚持以公开促改革。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">以预决算公开为抓手促进财税体制改革和其他相关领域改革，为实现政府治理体系和治理能力现代化提供动力。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">二、组织保障<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">（一）成立经信委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开工作领导小组，委主要领导任组长，其他领导任组员。对单位预决算信息公开工作进行指导、监督和检查。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（二）财务科在</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经信委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开工作领导小组指导下负责委预决算信息公开工作。其他科室根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">预决算公开任务分解予以配合。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">（三）监察审计室</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">在</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经信委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开工作领导小组指导下负责做好部门预决算信息公开后对社会公众的解释说明、答复工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（四）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">办公室负责</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">通过</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">中国昆山门户网站公开专栏进行</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">信息公开。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 29pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">三、预决算公开任务分解</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（一）经信委预算公开工作：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制部门预算表包括：部门收支预算总表、财政拨款支出预算表（按功能分类到项级）、财政拨款基本支出预算表（按经济分类到款级）、一般公共预算机关运行经费预算表、财政拨款政府性基金支出预算表、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费、会议费、培训费支出预算表、政府采购预算表等</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">张表</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制部门预算说明：部门预算安排情况</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">说明应包括部门年度收支预算安排情况；对</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: -0.5pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: -0.5pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: -0.5pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: -0.5pt; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费预算总额和分项数额增减变化的原因进行说明；</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">对重大项目资金安排或可能引起社会公众关注的预算安排，结合工作任务和事业发展目标加以阐述；对重要指标进行上下年度的比较和分析；（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）编制名词解释：对</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">预算表中的相关专业名称进行解释说明。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）汇总整理人事科、办公室提供的相关信息，完成预算公开的编制。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>2、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">办公室负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）为预算公开的编制提供当年度部门主要工作任务及下一年度工作目标等相关材料。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）编制政府采购预算草表，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">应包括专项名称、经济科目、采购物品名称、采购组织形式、预算安排等内容。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">并</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">对各政府采购项目应就项目用途、采购方式进行说明</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>3、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">人事科负责提供</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">部门职责、机构设置、编制现状等信息。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>4、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">委相关科室</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">负责提供</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定需要的其他资料。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; BACKGROUND: white; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">（二）经信委决算公开工作</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制部门决算表包括：部门收支决算总表、财政拨款支出决算表（按功能分类到项级）、财政拨款基本支出决算表（按经济分类到款级）、一般公共预算机关运行经费决算表、政府性基金预算财政拨款收支决算表、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费、会议费、培训费支出决算表、政府采购决算表等</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">张表。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制部门决算说明：部门决算情况说明应包括部门决算年度收支情况、财政拨款预算执行情况和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费、会议费、培训费、机关运行经费、政府采购支出决算情况及其说明；</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费决算公开要说明因公出国（境）团组数及人数，公务用车购置数及保有量，国内公务接待的批次、人数、经费总额以及</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">三公</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">经费增减变化原因等情况；会议费、培训费决算公开要说明召开会议和组织培训的次数和人数等相关明细信息。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制名词解释：名词解释主要对部门公开决算表中的相关专业名称进行解释说明。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）汇总整理人事科、办公室提供的相关信息，完成决算公开编制。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face=Calibri> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>2、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">办公室负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）为决算编制提供当年度部门主要工作完成情况。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）统计</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">因公出国（境）团组数及人数；公务用车购置数及保有量；国内公务接待的批次、人数，并将相关数据报送财务科汇总。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>3、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">人事科负责提供</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">部门职责、机构设置、编制现状等信息。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face=Calibri>4、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">委相关科室</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">负责提供</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定需要的其他资料。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; BACKGROUND: white; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">（三）经信委专项资金分配等信息公开（涉密项目除外）。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科负责审核汇总相关业务科室的专项资金分配等信息，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定编制</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">完成经信委专项资金分配等信息公开工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、企业服务科负责整理纳入市级政府部门专项资金管理清单的专项资金分配等信息报送财务科。对于实行因素法分配的项目，需提供分配因素、权重及分配结果；对于实行申报制的项目，需提供项目申报指南、审核程序、分配结果等；其他项目也应该及时提供分配结果。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（四）经信委采购信息公开（涉密项目除外）。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科：负责审核汇总办公室提供的相关政府采购信息，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">编制完成经信委采购信息公开工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、办公室：负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）按照《关于做好政府采购信息公开工作的通知》（苏财购〔</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2015</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">〕</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>51</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">号）要求，做好采购项目信息及法律、法规、规章规定应当公开的政府采购信息公开。在采购活动开始前，在采购文件中公开项目采购预算，采购尚未确定项目预算金额的，可不公开具体预算金额；采购活动完成后，公开中标、成交结果和政府采购合同。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）按采购进程，通过公共交易平台等网站及时公开。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（五）经信委预算绩效信息公开。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科：负责审核汇总相关业务科室的绩效预算信息，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">编制完成经信委预算绩效信息公开工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、投资与规划科、新兴产业发展科、科技与质量科、资源节约与综合利用科等科室：负责（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）编制项目预算绩效目标草表，报送财务科审核。应包括项目基本信息、项目绩效目标、项目绩效评价指标与标准值（即按绩效目标申报表表式内容编制），具体格式见财政局提供的样表。（</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">）撰写绩效评价初步结果，并报送财务科。应包括试点项目基本情况、绩效评价组织实施情况、项目绩效情况、项目管理成就、存在的问题和进一步加强项目管理的措施和建议等（即按绩效评价报告撰写提纲格式内容撰写）。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">（六）经信委资产信息公开。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、财务科：负责审核汇总办公室提供的资产信息，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt">预决算信息公开管理</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">规定</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">编制完成经信委资产信息公开工作。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">、办公室：负责统计车辆信息、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>200</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin">万元以上大型设备信息，其他固定资产信息。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
